== 反应==
氟锑酸加热到40 °C下分解，生成氟化氢气体和五氟化锑液体。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Oelderik|first1=Jan|date=December 1966|title=Werkwijze ter bereiding van halogeenverbindingen van vijfwaardig antimoon|journal=[[Netherlands_Patent_Application|Netherlands Patent Application]]|volume=NL 6508096 A}}</ref>

== 應用 ==
{{main|超強酸#應用}}
氟锑酸使其几乎可以[[质子化|质子化]]所有的[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]。它与[[异丁烷|异丁烷]]和[[新戊烷|新戊烷]]反应会生成相应的[[碳正离子|碳正离子]]：<ref>{{cite journal | author = Bickel, A. F.; Gaasbeek, C. J.; Hogeveen, H.; Oelderik, J. M.; Platteeuw, J. C. | title = Chemistry and spectroscopy in strongly acidic solutions: reversible reaction between aliphatic carbonium ions and hydrogen | journal = [[Chemical_Communications|Chemical Communications]] | year = 1967 | volume = 1967 | pages = 634–5 | doi = 10.1039/C19670000634}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Hogeveen, H.; Bickel, A. F. | title = Chemistry and spectroscopy in strongly acidic solutions: electrophilic substitution at alkane-carbon by protons | journal = [[Chemical_Communications|Chemical Communications]] | year = 1967 | volume = 1967 | pages = 635–6 | doi = 10.1039/C19670000635}}</ref>
:<chem>(CH3)3CH + H+ -> (CH3)3C+ + H2</chem>
:<chem>(CH3)4C + H+ -> (CH3)3C+ + CH4</chem>

== 危險性 ==
氟銻酸會與水起強烈甚至爆炸性的反應，而且它会與目前已知几乎所有的溶剂发生反應。<ref name=Olah/>能溶解氟銻酸的[[溶劑|溶劑]]有[[磺酰氟氯|磺酰氟氯]]（SO<sub>2</sub>ClF）、液态[[二氧化硫|二氧化硫]]及[[氟氯烃|氟氯烃]]。盛<chem>HF - SbF5</chem>的容器可用[[聚四氟乙烯|特氟龍]]製造。

